{"id":34529,"date":"2024-01-24T16:34:00","date_gmt":"2022-05-24T11:04:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=34529"},"modified":"2023-03-31T15:12:45","modified_gmt":"2023-03-31T09:42:45","slug":"small-dining-table","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/dining-room-interiors\/small-dining-table\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Small Dining Table Ideas That Win Big Compliments"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Save space smartly and leave guests wonderstruck with these small dining table ideas. Read on.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It\u2019s been several years now since most Indian families transitioned from traditional joint families to nuclear setups. Regardless, our philosophy of \u2018Atithi Devo Bhava\u2019 \u2014 treating guests like God \u2014 remains intact. After all, there\u2019s a certain warmth associated with expressing love through food. And at Design Cafe, we make it a point to celebrate that warm feeling through home interiors. Our designers bring you several innovative <strong>small dining table<\/strong> models to choose from, depending on your needs. Whatever you pick, one thing that\u2019s for sure is that you\u2019ll be bringing home a conversation starter. So, ready to check out our fabulous, custom and space-saving modular small dining table designs?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Dining Table Design For A Quick Brekkie<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The morning madness can make it difficult to set food on a formal dining table and clean up later. So, we designed a kitchen pull-out table as a life-saver for couples during rush-hour mornings. With the cooktop, the sleek and spacious marble counter and the breakfast table in proximity, you save time on all fronts \u2014 cooking, setting the food and cleaning the dining space. And if you want some spices or additional cutlery in the midst of a meal, the overhead cabinets and underneath pull-out drawers are within quick reach in this modular kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180746\/small-dining-table-design-for-a-quick-brekkie.jpg\" alt=\"Small dining table design for a quick brekkie\" class=\"wp-image-34530\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180746\/small-dining-table-design-for-a-quick-brekkie.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180746\/small-dining-table-design-for-a-quick-brekkie-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180746\/small-dining-table-design-for-a-quick-brekkie-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180746\/small-dining-table-design-for-a-quick-brekkie-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A time-saving kitchen pull-out small dining table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Dining Table Ideas In The Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re opting for an <em>island modular kitchen<\/em>, then the granite-top breakfast counter will fill in for a <strong>small dining table set<\/strong> \u2013 saving you ample space. What makes the breakfast counter multi-functional is that it can be used as a free-standing cabinet for additional storage and as an extra surface for your cooking and work-from-home needs. This design is ideal for families with children so that cooking, conversations and eating can happen in an intimate yet comfortable setting \u2013 be it on a busy day or a lazy weekend.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180745\/small-dining-table-set-ideas-in-the-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Small dining table set ideas in the kitchen in granite\" class=\"wp-image-34531\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180745\/small-dining-table-set-ideas-in-the-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180745\/small-dining-table-set-ideas-in-the-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180745\/small-dining-table-set-ideas-in-the-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180745\/small-dining-table-set-ideas-in-the-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Versatile small dining table in granite<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Small Living Room With A Dining Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When looking for a <strong>dining table for small spaces<\/strong>, a foldable table is a great option. With our creative and functional designs, the foldable table can be tucked into a wall to double up as a wall-mounted cabinet! Maximum utility and maximum space-saving. That\u2019s what we call a win-win. This kind of drop-down table with a combined cabinet is also the most efficient design when you\u2019re exploring <strong>small living room ideas with a TV and dining table <\/strong>for your home. Whether you want to accommodate it in a small space or want to make an empty nest less gloomy, a drop-down dining table in a popping colour works best.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180743\/small-living-room-with-a-dining-tables-for-small-spaces.jpg\" alt=\"Small living room with a dining tables for small spaces that makes room for guests\" class=\"wp-image-34532\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180743\/small-living-room-with-a-dining-tables-for-small-spaces.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180743\/small-living-room-with-a-dining-tables-for-small-spaces-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180743\/small-living-room-with-a-dining-tables-for-small-spaces-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180743\/small-living-room-with-a-dining-tables-for-small-spaces-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An expandable table that makes room for guests<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Folding Dining Table For Small Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most families scouting for a dining table typically tend to buy a four-seater table, even if their living space is compact. But with the arrival of custom modular furniture, a traditional four-seater table is redundant. Say hello to Design Cafe\u2019s expandable dining table that\u2019s jaw-dropping in aesthetics and functionality. Our drop-leaf two-seater dining table can be expanded to accommodate up to six guests! With foldable chairs that can be stored within the table, this <strong>small folding dining table<\/strong> will be the smartest addition to your living space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180742\/folding-dining-table-for-small-spaces-modern.jpg\" alt=\"Folding expandable dining table for small spaces modern with aesthetics and functionality\" class=\"wp-image-34533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180742\/folding-dining-table-for-small-spaces-modern.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180742\/folding-dining-table-for-small-spaces-modern-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180742\/folding-dining-table-for-small-spaces-modern-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180742\/folding-dining-table-for-small-spaces-modern-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An expandable table that makes room for guests<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A 2-In-1 Folding Dining Table Design For Small Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern ready-to-occupy homes rarely have separate dining and living areas. The good news is \u2014 modern problems inspire modern solutions. Our multi-functional folding dining table with open shelves will come to your rescue. The drop-leaf table serves your dining needs adequately at mealtimes. At other times, you may use it to store handy essentials for the living room \u2013 quick bites for TV time, mobile chargers or even bedding for an overnight guest or couch surfer. If not the living room, it\u2019s also a practical <strong>small kitchen table design<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180740\/a-2-in-1-folding-small-dining-table-design-for-small-spaces.jpg\" alt=\"A 2-in-1 folding small dining table design for small spaces with storage shelves\" class=\"wp-image-34534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180740\/a-2-in-1-folding-small-dining-table-design-for-small-spaces.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180740\/a-2-in-1-folding-small-dining-table-design-for-small-spaces-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180740\/a-2-in-1-folding-small-dining-table-design-for-small-spaces-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180740\/a-2-in-1-folding-small-dining-table-design-for-small-spaces-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A folding dining table with storage shelves<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Four-Seater Dining Table For Small Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An elegant wall-mounted crockery unit that can extend into a <strong>four-seater small dining table<\/strong>! With this innovative dining table<strong> <\/strong>in veneer finish,<strong> <\/strong>we solve the predicament of many households who want a larger storage unit for their fancy china. The foldable tabletop effortlessly blends into the crockery unit when not in use. It also features an attached tall closed cabinet on the side to ensure that the table doesn\u2019t expose the entire unit.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180739\/small-dining-table-4-seater-for-small-spaces.jpg\" alt=\"Small dining table 4 seater for small spaces with elegant wall-mounted crockery unit\" class=\"wp-image-34535\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180739\/small-dining-table-4-seater-for-small-spaces.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180739\/small-dining-table-4-seater-for-small-spaces-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180739\/small-dining-table-4-seater-for-small-spaces-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180739\/small-dining-table-4-seater-for-small-spaces-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Bespoke multipurpose wall-mounted dining table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Charming Small Dining Table Near The Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the many advantages of a modular kitchen is that, based on its layout and the number of occupants in the house, it negates the need for a dining space. A great example is this G-shaped kitchen. The design makes room for a portion of the countertop to be used as a dining table without taking up additional floor space. The cabinets below the countertop enable safe storage and quick access to essential tableware for everyday dining. The windows and pendant lights allow sufficient lighting, making the G-shaped kitchen a charming date spot too!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180735\/a-charming-small-dining-table-near-the-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"A charming small kitchen dining table near the kitchen with a kitchen countertop\" class=\"wp-image-34536\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180735\/a-charming-small-dining-table-near-the-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180735\/a-charming-small-dining-table-near-the-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180735\/a-charming-small-dining-table-near-the-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180735\/a-charming-small-dining-table-near-the-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A kitchen countertop cum small dining table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There\u2019s no dearth of designs when it comes to multipurpose furniture, including a <strong>small dining table<\/strong>. What you really need is a team that understands your requirements and preferences. If you\u2019re ready to meet our team, book your appointment<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\"> here<\/a>. If you wish to look for more designs, do continue to explore our<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/\"> blog<\/a> section.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/